# DESIGN_WORKPLAN.md

## Purpose

Define the design-stage workplan for {{ project.name }}.

This optional template is Markdown-only. It does not authorize runtime implementation, source code, live target writes, external mutation, CI, or project-specific domain content.

## Scope

- Design-only purpose and phase objective.
- Candidate design outputs.
- Source-use decisions for this phase.
- Exit criteria before implementation planning.
- Open risks and owner-review dependencies.

## Source Use

| source row | decision | allowed handling |
|---|---|---|
| SRC-### | usable for design summary | Use category-level summaries only |
| SRC-### | owner review required | Do not use until owner accepts, revises, or defers |
| SRC-### | excluded from repo | Do not use in target content |

Owner-review sources must not be used until the owner records accept, revise, or defer. Excluded sources must stay outside repository and generated target content.

## Prohibited Content

- Runtime implementation.
- Application source code.
- C# source, solution, project, XAML, build assets, scripts, binaries, or executable packaging.
- PLC/device code.
- Live target write support or external mutation.
- GitHub Actions or cloud CI.
- Raw source bulk copy.
- IP, port, tag value, live parameter, secret, credential, private input, live config, or equipment detail.
- Downstream-specific content except placeholders and generalized summaries.

## Approval Boundary

Design work may start only after the relevant design-stage entry approval is recorded. Implementation planning, runtime work, live-write behavior, and example/profile creation require separate explicit approval.

## Candidate Outputs

| output | purpose | status |
|---|---|---|
| CONCEPT_BOUNDARY.md | Define design-only boundary | PENDING |
| CATEGORY_MAP.md | Map generalized categories | PENDING |
| SYNTHETIC_FIXTURE_PLAN.md | Plan synthetic fixture categories | PENDING |
| ACCEPTANCE_EVIDENCE_PLAN.md | Plan evidence coverage | PENDING |
| OPEN_QUESTIONS.md | Track unresolved owner questions | PENDING |
| DESIGN_REVIEW_RECORD.md | Record design-stage review | PENDING |

## Review Checklist

- Scope is design-only and documentation-only.
- Source-use decisions are explicit.
- Owner-review sources are not used before accept/revise/defer.
- Excluded sources are not used.
- Prohibited content is absent.
- Exit criteria are recorded before implementation planning.
